Summary: Coinbase (COIN) analyzed 1 bill with no direct impacts and 1 indirect impact, resulting in minimal direct risk but slight indirect regulatory exposure. Overall risk: low.
SummaryKeypoints: REGULATION (EU) 2024/1689 OF THE EUROPEAN PARLIAMENT AND OF THE COUNCIL affects supplier providers of general-purpose AI models (not specified) through fine The legislation specifies: "The Commission may impose on providers of general-purpose AI models fines not exceeding 3 % of their annual total worldwide turnover in the preceding financial year or EUR 15 000 000, whichever is higher."
